# Intentionally (almost) empty.
#
# Prettier defaults its --ignore-path to [".gitignore", ".prettierignore"]. Our
# .gitignore lists `generated/` (so generated output isn't committed), which
# would also make `prettier --check generated/` silently skip every file. The
# harness passes `--ignore-path .prettierignore` so this file REPLACES that
# default list, and Prettier actually checks the generated files.
